Package: magmaan.experiments
Title: Shared Helpers for Magmaan Experiments
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Jonas", "Moss", email = "jonas.moss@bi.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Small non-statistical helpers for repo-local magmaan experiments:
    path discovery, result CSV writing, metadata capture, package checks, and
    simple argument parsing utilities, plus explicit experiment-local cache
    helpers for reusable simulation calibration artifacts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
